Syntax-BERT: Improving Pre-trained Transformers with Syntax Trees
标题：语法-BERT：用语法树改进预先训练的转换器
作者：Jiangang Bai,Yujing Wang,Yiren Chen,Yaming Yang,Jing Bai,Jing Yu,Yunhai Tong
机构：Peking University, Beijing, China, Microsoft Research Asia, Beijing, China, Institute of Information Engineering, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Beijing, China, yujing,iie.ac.cn
备注：EACL2021
链接：https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.04350
一只好奇怎么将语法树的信息加入到神经网络的训练中，之前的论文：Linguistically-Informed Self-Attention for Semantic Role Labeling通过多任务学习，前面层学习为谓词识别和pos任务，结合了语法和transformer用于SRL。
这篇论文使用语法树提升预训练模型的效果。

2021-03-10

Self-supervised Regularization for Text Classification
标题：自监督正则化在文本分类中的应用
作者：Meng Zhou,Zechen Li,Pengtao Xie
机构：Shanghai Jiao Tong University Northeastern University, UC San Diego
备注：15 pages, 3 figures, to be published in Transactions of the Association for Computational Linguistics
链接：https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.05231
